        "richtext_Pdk9a9": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><strong>A Ma Maniére and Jordan Brand present </strong><em><strong>Built For This: Homecoming</strong></em><strong> — a chapter rooted in reflection, gratitude, and earned acknowledgment. This moment honors the journey, the weight of the work, and the stories that shaped it. Homecoming reframes celebration not as an escape, but as a truth revealed: every step meant something, every sacrifice left its mark. The work mattered—and now, the feeling is the proof.<br/></strong><em><strong><br/></strong></em><strong>The A Ma Maniére x Air Jordan 4 “Dark Mocha” is a refined expression of craftsmanship. Dark mocha nubuck brings richness and depth, while tonal hardware and reworked wings and netting create a clean, architectural feel. Visible Air cushioning keeps the silhouette grounded in comfort, and the signature quilted lining adds a final layer of sophistication true to A Ma Maniére’s design ethos.</strong><em><strong><br/><br/></strong></em><strong>Releasing alongside the footwear are A Ma Maniére’s accessories: the Leather Tote and Leather Pouch in soft full-grain leather, the Signature Scarf featuring a bandana-inspired pattern. All accessories will also be offered through raffle. The nylon outerwear collection includes the Puffer Jacket, Coaches Jacket, Nylon Varsity, Nylon Jacket and Nylon Pants, each designed with smooth finishes, refined lines and silhouettes made for everyday movement.<br/><br/></strong></p><p></p>",
            "text_color": "#eaeaea"
          }
        },
        "button_jJg4wY": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
